Italy Must Amend ‘Grave’ Budget Error, Merkel Ally Tells Paper

-- B y   B r i a n   P a r k i n
-- 
2011-09-23T11:41:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-23/italy-must-amend-grave-budget-error-merkel-ally-tells-paper.html
Italy must amend its “grave
error” in watering down planned budget cuts in August and
redouble its efforts to rein in spending, said  Peter Altmaier , a
senior lawmaker from  Chancellor Angela Merkel ’s  Christian
Democrats , cited in an interview in the Passauer Neue Presse
newspaper.  The move highlighted “how serious the situation is” in the
euro region, said Altmaier, who is his party’s executive
director in parliament.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Brian Parkin at 
 bparkin@bloomberg.net  